  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Service Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>We exist to enrich your life. We help you live smarter, happier and greener. Creating huge benefits for Customers is our priority. We specialise in smart control solutions for residential, commercial, hospitality and industrial segments. We offer consultancy, integration, development, installation and project management. We deliver quality products and systems from ABB, LUTRON and STEINEL.</p><ul><li>[www.intellihub.com.sg](http: //www.intellihub.com.sg/)</li></ul><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Join our team as a Service Technician/Electrician to install, service, and troubleshoot lighting control systems for residential and commercial clients, delivering excellent customer service in a fast-paced environment.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Install and configure lighting control systems to meet project specifications</li><li>Perform system maintenance, repairs, and troubleshooting to ensure reliable operation</li><li>Collaborate with project engineers and designers to complete installations efficiently and accurately</li><li>Provide on-site training to clients on operating their lighting control systems</li><li>Maintain accurate records of completed work and assist with system documentation</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Hold Higher Nitec or equivalent technical certifications in electrical or related fields</li><li>Demonstrate at least 1 year of relevant experience in electrical work</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Possess hands-on experience with lighting control systems</li><li>Apply strong troubleshooting and problem-solving skills in electrical system contexts</li><li>Work effectively both independently and as part of a team</li><li>Willingness to travel for on-site installations and support</li></ul>",
